snippet.title: GOD EATER: Resurrection - Launch Trailer | PS4, Vita
snippet.description:
Defy The Gods starting today!

GOD EATER: Resurrection launches on 6/28 for PS4 and Vita. Pre-order GOD EATER 2: Rage Burst (PS4) now to get a digital PSN voucher for GOD EATER: Resurrection (PS4) and DLC costumes from SWORD ART ONLINE: HOLLOW REALIZATION, TALES OF ZESTIRIA and TOKYO GHOUL.

PlayStation Store Page: https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/games/god-eater-2-rage-burst/cid=UP0700-CUSA03305_00-PS4GE2RAGEBURST0

Stay up-to-date here: 
God Eater on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/godeaterden 
God Eater on Twitter: https://twitter.com/godeaterden 
Official Game Site: http://www.god-eater.com/
